org.apache.batik.dom.util
Interface XMLHttpRequest

public interface XMLHttpRequest

An interface for objects that can fetch HTTP resources. This interface will likely move to a different package at some point (perhaps org.w3c.dom.webapi).

See Also:
The XMLHttpRequest Object
